Author: Oracle Component Name: JKM Sybase ASE Consistent Component Version: 10.1.3.1 Compatibility: ODI 10.1.3.5.0 and above
Description: Journalizing Knowledge Module This JKM provides consistent journalizing procedures on Sybase ASE tables It is mandatory to define a primary Key for each datastore in the CDC set.
Quick Start: 1. In your Model choose the consitency journalizing mode 2. choose the JKM Sybase ASE Consistent 3. Add datastores to the CDC set 4. Start the journal
Known Limitations: - When starting the journal on a model, tables no longer in the set are unjournalized, tables missing from the set are journalized. - If the table is already journalized and is present in another model, the current journal data will be lost and the table is transfered to the new journal set. - This Knowledge Module creates triggers on your source tables. Be sure to validate the scalability of your applications before releasing your developments in your production systems. - In particular if you already have triggers on your table, this JKM will replace your own code, because Sybase don't accepte more than one trigger for each type (INS,UPD,DEL)
Requirements: The database user that is used to connect to the staging area must have at least the following privileges on the target table: SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE, CREATE TRIGGER, CREATE VIEW The database user that is used to connect to the staging area must have at least the following privileges: DROP ANY TABLE, CREATE ANY TABLE

updCmd = """ update <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> set SUBS.MAX_WINDOW_ID = CDC.CUR_WINDOW_ID, SUBS.MAX_WINDOW_ID_INS = CDC.CUR_WINDOW_ID_INS, SUBS.MAX_WINDOW_ID_DEL = CDC.CUR_WINDOW_ID_DEL from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> SUBS, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SET_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> CDC where CDC.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and SUBS.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and SUBS.CDC_SUBSCRIBER = ? """
# Prepare the update prepUpdStmt = myCon.prepareStatement(updCmd)
# Execute it for each subscriber for sbs in lstSbs: prepUpdStmt.setString(1, sbs) nbRows = prepUpdStmt.executeUpdate()
prepUpdStmt.close()
# Commit the updates myCon.commit()

updCmd = """ update <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> set MIN_WINDOW_ID = MAX_WINDOW_ID_INS where CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and CDC_SUBSCRIBER = ? """
# Prepare the update prepUpdStmt = myCon.prepareStatement(updCmd)
# Execute it for each subscriber for sbs in lstSbs: prepUpdStmt.setString(1, sbs) nbRows = prepUpdStmt.executeUpdate()
prepUpdStmt.close()
# Commit the updates myCon.commit()

/* Delete rows from journalizing tables that are useless for each subscriber */ delete from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_FULL_NAME")%> where WINDOW_ID <= ( select min(SUBS.MIN_WINDOW_ID) from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> SUBS where SUBS.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' )

import java.sql as sql import java.lang as lang
# Connect to the Source Database ie the one that hosts the journalized tables myCon = odiRef.getJDBCConnection("SRC")
# Create the list of Subscribers for a CDC Set lstSbs = [] <%= odiRef.getSubscriberList("" , "lstSbs.append('[SUBSCRIBER]')", "\n", "") %>

create table <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo( "CDC_SUBS_TABLE" )%> /* This table is created in the work physical schema set as default for the Data server */ ( CDC_SET_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR" , "255", "0" )%> not null, /* Name of the CDC Set (Sunopsis model code) */ CDC_SUBSCRIBER <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR" , "35", "0" )%> not null, /* Name of the subscriber who subscribed to the CDC Set */ CDC_REFDATE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_DATE")%> not null, /* Last update of the record */ MIN_WINDOW_ID <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "20")%> not null, /* Window Ids under this one should be ignored */ MAX_WINDOW_ID <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "20")%> not null, /* Maximum Window Id used by this subscription */ MAX_WINDOW_ID_DEL <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "20")%> not null, /* Maximum Window Id to take into consideration when looking at consistency for deletes */ MAX_WINDOW_ID_INS <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "20")%> not null, /* Maximum Window Id to take into consideration when looking at consistency for inserts / updates */ CDC_ROW_COUNT <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "10")%> not null, /* Number of rows in the journalizing tables for this subscription */ constraint PK_SNP_CDC_SBS primary key (CDC_SET_NAME, CDC_SUBSCRIBER) )

create table <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo( "CDC_SET_TABLE" )%> /* This table is created in the work physical schema set as default for the Data server */ ( CDC_SET_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR" , "255", "0" )%> not null, /* Name of the CDC Set (Sunopsis model code) */ CUR_WINDOW_ID <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "20")%> not null, /* Last window Id that has been used */ CUR_WINDOW_ID_DEL <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "20")%> not null, /* Last Window Id used to compute delete consitency */ CUR_WINDOW_ID_INS <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "20")%> not null, /* Last Window Id used to compute inert / update consitency */ RETRIEVE_DATA TEXT null, /* Command to execute in order to retrieve the journal data (used by the SnpsRetrieveJournalData API) */ REFRESH_ROW_COUNT TEXT null, /* Command to execute in order to refresh the row count(used by the SnpsRefreshJournalData API) */ constraint PK_SNP_CDC_SET primary key (CDC_SET_NAME) )

create table <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> ( CDC_SET_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR" , "255")%> not null, /* Name of the CDC Set (Sunopsis model code) */ FULL_TABLE_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "255")%> not null, /* Complete name of the journalized table */ FULL_DATA_VIEW <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "255")%> not null, /* Complete name of the journalizing data view */ RETRIEVE_DATA TEXT null, /* Command to execute to retrieve the journal data (used by the SnpsRetrieveJournalData API) */ REFRESH_ROW_COUNT TEXT null, /* Command to execute to refresh the row count (used by the SnpsRefresh RowCount API) */ constraint PK_SNP_CDC_TBL primary key (FULL_TABLE_NAME) )

create table <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_OBJECTS_TABLE")%> ( FULL_TABLE_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "255")%> not null, /* Complete name of the journalized table */ CDC_OBJECT_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "35")%> not null, /* Type of the object in the CDC framework */ FULL_OBJECT_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "255")%> not null, /* Complete name of the object */ DB_OBJECT_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "35")%> null, /* RDBMS type of the object (ex : TABLE, VIEW, TRIGGER) */ constraint PK_SNP_CDC_OBJ primary key (FULL_TABLE_NAME, CDC_OBJECT_TYPE) )

update <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SET_TABLE")%> set RETRIEVE_DATA = NULL, REFRESH_ROW_COUNT = 'update <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> set CDC_ROW_COUNT = 0 where CDC_SUBSCRIBER = ''$$SUBSCRIBER_NAME$$'' and CDC_SET_NAME = ''<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>''' where CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>'

insCmd = """ insert into <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> ( CDC_SET_NAME, CDC_SUBSCRIBER, CDC_REFDATE, MIN_WINDOW_ID, MAX_WINDOW_ID, MAX_WINDOW_ID_DEL, MAX_WINDOW_ID_INS, CDC_ROW_COUNT ) select /* CDC_SET_NAME */ '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>', /* CDC_SUBSCRIBER */ ?, /* CDC_REFDATE */ getdate(), /* MIN_WINDOW_ID */ CDC.CUR_WINDOW_ID, /* MAX_WINDOW_ID */ -1, /* MAX_WINDOW_ID_DEL */ -1, /* MAX_WINDOW_ID_INS */ -1, /* CDC_ROW_COUNT */ 0 from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SET_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> CDC where CDC.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' """
selCmd = """ select count('X') from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> CDC where CDC.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and CDC.CDC_SUBSCRIBER = ? """
# Prepare the statements prepInsStmt = myCon.prepareStatement(insCmd) prepSelStmt = myCon.prepareStatement(selCmd)
# Execute for each subscriber for sbs in lstSbs: prepSelStmt.setString(1, sbs) rs = prepSelStmt.executeQuery() rs.next() nbSubs = rs.getInt(1) if (nbSubs == 0): prepInsStmt.setString(1, sbs) nbRows = prepInsStmt.executeUpdate()
prepInsStmt.close() prepSelStmt.close()
# Commit the updates myCon.commit()
Delete table from CDC Objects table

/* This query returns a row for each journalizing trigger, view or table if the table is no longer a part of the CDC Set */ select OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_TYPE, OBJ.FULL_OBJECT_NAME <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_NAME from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_OBJECTS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> OBJ, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> CDC where CDC.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and CDC.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME and OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE in ('VIEW', 'TABLE')

/* This query returns a row for each journalizing trigger, view or table if the table is no longer a part of the CDC Set */ select OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_TYPE, OBJ.FULL_OBJECT_NAME <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_NAME from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_OBJECTS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> OBJ, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> CDC where CDC.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and CDC.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME and OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE = 'TRIGGER'

/* This query returns a row for each journalizing trigger, view or table if the table is no longer a part of the CDC Set */ select OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_TYPE, OBJ.FULL_OBJECT_NAME <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_NAME from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_OBJECTS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> OBJ, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> CDC where CDC.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and CDC.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME and OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE in ('VIEW', 'TABLE') and not exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getObjectName("L" ,"SNP_TMP_TABLE_LIST" , "W")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> TMP where TMP.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME )

/* This query returns a row for each journalizing trigger, view or table if the table is no longer a part of the CDC Set */ select OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_TYPE, OBJ.FULL_OBJECT_NAME <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> DB_OBJECT_NAME from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_OBJECTS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> OBJ, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> CDC where CDC.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and CDC.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME and OBJ.DB_OBJECT_TYPE = 'TRIGGER' and not exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getObjectName("L" ,"SNP_TMP_TABLE_LIST" , "W")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> TMP where TMP.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME )

select FULL_TABLE_NAME <%= odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD") %> FULL_TABLE_NAME from <%=odiRef.getObjectName("L" ,"SNP_TMP_TABLE_LIST" , "W")%> <%= odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD") %> TMP where TMP.FULL_TABLE_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("FULL_TABLE_NAME")%>' and not exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_OBJECTS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> OBJ, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> TBL where TBL.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME and TBL.FULL_TABLE_NAME = TMP.FULL_TABLE_NAME and TBL.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and OBJ.FULL_OBJECT_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_FULL_NAME")%>' and OBJ.CDC_OBJECT_TYPE = 'JRN_FULL_NAME' )

create view <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_WORK_SCHEMA")%>.<%=odiRef.getInfo( "JRN_VIEW")%> /* This view is created in the work physical schema of the current Data server */ as select distinct case when (<%=odiRef.getColList("", "convert(varchar,TARG.[COL_NAME])", " + ", "", "PK")%>) is null then 'D' else 'I' end <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> JRN_FLAG, getdate() <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> JRN_DATE, /* For V3 compatibility */ SUB.CDC_SUBSCRIBER <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD")%> JRN_SUBSCRIBER, /* Renamed for V3 compatibility */ <%=odiRef.getColList("", "JRN.[COL_NAME]			" + odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD") + " [COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "PK")%>, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "TARG.[COL_NAME]			" + odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD") + " [COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "NOT PK")%> from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_FULL_NAME")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> JRN, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> SUB, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("FULL_TABLE_NAME")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> TARG where <%=odiRef.getColList("", "TARG.[COL_NAME]	=* JRN.[COL_NAME]", "
and	", "", "PK")%> and SUB.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and JRN.WINDOW_ID > SUB.MIN_WINDOW_ID and JRN.WINDOW_ID <= SUB.MAX_WINDOW_ID_DEL and not ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "TARG.[COL_NAME] is not null", "
		and	", "", "PK")%> and JRN.WINDOW_ID > SUB.MAX_WINDOW_ID_INS )

create trigger <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_WORK_SCHEMA")%>.<%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_TRIGGER")%>_D on <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("FULL_TABLE_NAME")%> for delete as begin insert into <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_FULL_NAME")%> ( WINDOW_ID, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t\t\t", "", "PK")%> ) select NULL,/* WINDOW_ID */ <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t\t\t", "", "PK")%> from deleted end

select FULL_TABLE_NAME <%= odiRef.getInfo("DEST_COL_ALIAS_WORD") %> FULL_TABLE_NAME from <%=odiRef.getObjectName("L" ,"SNP_TMP_TABLE_LIST" , "W")%> <%= odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD") %> TMP where TMP.FULL_TABLE_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("FULL_TABLE_NAME")%>' and not exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_OBJECTS_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> OBJ, <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> TBL where TBL.FULL_TABLE_NAME = OBJ.FULL_TABLE_NAME and TBL.FULL_TABLE_NAME = TMP.FULL_TABLE_NAME and TBL.CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and OBJ.FULL_OBJECT_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_FULL_TRIGGER")%>' and OBJ.CDC_OBJECT_TYPE = 'JRN_FULL_TRIGGER' )

delCmd = """ delete from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SUBS_TABLE")%> where CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and CDC_SUBSCRIBER = ? """
# Prepare the delete prepDelStmt = myCon.prepareStatement(delCmd)
# Execute it for each subscriber for sbs in lstSbs: prepDelStmt.setString(1, sbs) nbRows = prepDelStmt.executeUpdate()
prepDelStmt.close()
# Commit the updates myCon.commit()

delete from <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_TABLE_TABLE")%> where CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>' and FULL_TABLE_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("FULL_TABLE_NAME")%>'

/* Compulsory to prevent SnpsRetrieveData or other Extend window in parallel */ update <%=odiRef.getJrnInfo("CDC_SET_TABLE")%> set CUR_WINDOW_ID = CUR_WINDOW_ID + 2, CUR_WINDOW_ID_INS = CUR_WINDOW_ID + 1, CUR_WINDOW_ID_DEL = CUR_WINDOW_ID + 2 where CDC_SET_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getObjectName("L", odiRef.getJrnInfo("JRN_COD_MOD"), "D")%>'
